### ğŸ¨ (E) Use Tailwind or Bootstrap for Components

Tailwind is perfect for minimal, custom UI.
Bootstrap gives prebuilt components (cards, modals, grids).

You can combine both if careful â€” e.g. Tailwind for layout, Bootstrap for modals/forms.

Example with Tailwind card:

```tsx
